{"tid":324082,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"邦路斯同丹尼爾打交釀離祖記？","createTime":"2017-07-16T07:19:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-17T15:56:20.000Z","uid":32938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8cb7517609753ab3f2b009bdeb4cd855128f4b05","tid":324082,"uid":32938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T07:19:40.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=n5LJYnjb56BN7rXI7crcNE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=5509afb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】祖雲達斯前鋒文迪蘇傑透露，邦路斯與丹尼爾於歐聯決賽半場時講手，是兩人最終離開祖記的原因。<br />\n<br />\n此前有傳祖雲達斯在對皇家馬德里的歐聯決賽半場休息時，後衛邦路斯（Leonardo Bonucci）與隊友保羅戴巴拿於更衣室發生肢體衝突，前鋒文迪蘇傑（Mario Mandzukic）近日於訪問中揭開事件真相，但主角之一並非保羅戴巴拿，而是巴西翼衛丹尼爾（Dani Alves）。 據文迪蘇傑憶述，邦路斯與丹尼爾上季經常爭吵，祖記球員可謂司空見慣。而話說歐聯決賽半場時，丹尼爾在更衣室內大聲播放音樂及起舞，引起邦路斯不滿並著他馬上關掉音樂。丹尼爾卻不照做，還表示球隊若輸掉決賽，他仍有（為巴塞隆拿取得的）3枚歐聯冠軍獎牌，而邦路斯卻1枚也沒有。 邦路斯盛怒下向丹尼爾「叉頸」，並幾乎飽以拳頭，此時教練柯歷利走進來把兩人分開，並說道：「我不理是誰先動手，但你們兩人均會被踢出球會。」 從文迪蘇傑的口述版本，似乎亦印證了何故丹尼爾後來與祖雲達斯分手，而邦路斯則以4200萬歐元轉會費過檔AC米蘭。文迪蘇傑還表示：「這個決定十分明智，球隊可再次安靜及團結起來，爭取佳績。」"},{"pid":"43eeaa2dab9eaa52ce69e86a686a83f028dbecb6","tid":324082,"uid":14812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T07:22:37.000Z","msg":"丹狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"656faa7688cfb5e71481e32972cc241b859617f4","tid":324082,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T07:30:00.000Z","msg":"咁撚串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"871841aa16b7b78f6d57118495edc3d718e26986","tid":324082,"uid":100689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T07:32:02.000Z","msg":"往死裡打啦仲講咁多"},{"pid":"5ca2579e9a435aa5720da5869727b6c25795415f","tid":324082,"uid":3342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T07:33:50.000Z","msg":"咩source呀<br />\nNow幾時出埋呢d飛機文"},{"pid":"3896db25e83229b37f3d8bb54fe53c84c5cfecb3","tid":324082,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T07:35:31.000Z","msg":"分唔出潮文定新文"},{"pid":"d12ec21a80fa7bc8e8822d4f6cdba8647537f2b6","tid":324082,"uid":37240,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T07:37:24.000Z","msg":"仲以為往死裡打個篇潮文"},{"pid":"40de900943bc13a6dd767284105eb09f9d09f0f1","tid":324082,"uid":94182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T07:54:03.000Z","msg":"搞到我想睇多次往死裡打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗起洛賓個串樣打交好正"},{"pid":"6cc26b86752b672fba3067af69f492b0cb2e7107","tid":324082,"uid":11185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T10:17:10.000Z","msg":"以為有肉腸"},{"pid":"5883aebfdc4de1775565abcd0171d00ec2c803c6","tid":324082,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T10:37:42.000Z","msg":"DaniAlves串過馬撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c585b51d9734b34667e9a43f289228696a5a3167","tid":324082,"uid":14812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T10:39:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>DaniAlves串過馬撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢串得起 佢本身去祖都係養老<br />\n球會獎係巴塞捧到手軟"},{"pid":"f5924e349c4f9c9b1317975e20de3a8c393d2b14","tid":324082,"uid":3244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T10:41:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"48b85136ce82b351edf9ddae2dd460e307db3f6a","tid":324082,"uid":88461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T11:21:26.000Z","msg":"仲諗著係潮文，點知上now睇，真嘅屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88bc5e7774ad807c1f04d37202e72d02ad94579c","tid":324082,"uid":21028,"lik